LJ::Simple version 0.15
===========================

LJ::Simple is a simple perl API to LiveJournal. Currently it provides
the following functionality:

 o Login
 o Post journal entries
 o Synchronise journal entries
 o Edit journal entries
 o Delete journal entries
 o Get a list of users who consider the LJ user logged in as their friend
 o Get a list of the users the LJ user logged in considers a friend
 o See if the user's friend list has been updated

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires nothing other than the modules which come with the
standard perl 5.6.1 distribution.

If you have Digest::MD5 available then the code will make use of encrypted
passwords automatically.

The test target will use the LJ test account to do its work

